"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"金色财经报道，游戏巨头育碧（Ubisoft）已成为第一家涉足NFT世界的主要游戏公司。根据周二的公告，育碧推出了新平台Ubisoft Quartz的测试版，该平台允许用户获取可在游戏中使用的物品的NFT，例如武器、服装或车辆。Ubisoft Quartz将这些NFT称为“Digits”，并选择将这些NFT基于Tezos[区块链](https://www.bitcoin86.com/block/)\",\"timestamp\":1639060941,\"title\":\"游戏巨头育碧正通过新平台测试游戏内NFT\"},\"digest\":\"z7wspqy2QCBVkYqTvAl2X9K81P1yg5NWh_OD6nrcSOQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xca682d420dF454Ef5b879E0A4136356993E777Ef\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"f5ygZnG4902FRNN9j-nioskaFttFvoSescBe5F4EFQA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"awyHWqUEs6VsFH56Mmixzq_5MFtEhmsAaH4x2C8_urU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"TjR4rKSZViJmmXYPfODkl2pPWwKxHk8F4kzXFRymQ9clEaRORvmUN6rH49xvsAh5q6sjwmLWuP0sibvlAifcfQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x70b13a51d25ae59deaeea427ed89ce416c5060ac2debb1218e7024d5dfc76f10636a6c75f2819a0bf21b0f8c1a6d1c2ca1ffb2300cb0fb0c821652b60bd519371c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"f5ygZnG4902FRNN9j-nioskaFttFvoSescBe5F4EFQA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"awyHWqUEs6VsFH56Mmixzq_5MFtEhmsAaH4x2C8_urU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"z7wspqy2QCBVkYqTvAl2X9K81P1yg5NWh_OD6nrcSOQ\"}"